I did a rough update to the summary and setting section of the wiki.  I
haven&#39;t updated any of he sub pages but I eventually will.  As for many of
the inactive characters, I&#39;m thinking of either creating a separate list or
moving them off to the continuum characters list so we can more or less have
a list of currently active characters.

The maximals have more or less consolidated.  We have a small group of
Bushido Predecons that were active, the other group Iron Skulls, haven&#39;t
really done anything.  I was thinking they might both align with Hydras, but
then again the Bushido&#39;s sense of honor might make them reluctant to follow
him.  The watchers can continue as they are, since they&#39;ve always been
background characters; right now they&#39;re keeping an eye on the Ark.

-Kraftlos


