but I have been sporatically reading some of the posts I have missed.

My core characters would be: Cyclonus & Scourge, Marauder, Legacy. I am also
keeping Rodimus for the moment to work out a few things with Airly.

I am also utilizing other characters that I was temping before I left such
as: Lord Elder, and Zarak/Skorponok to keep some plot elements running, but
they may fade back into the backround as things quiet a little. And of
course there were the minions I left in NPC status and Myrmidon who is in
the background.

You will probrably note that as time goes along some of these other
characters I play will fade into and out of the backround, and I will only
be playing a few at a time as people need RP partners or events unfold. For
example, Legacy tends to stay at the Ark for the most part, and will
eventually return there unless something happens to change that.

If anyone wants to run one of the minions NPC&#39;s or any of the characters I
am temping, they are more than welcome, so long as they let me know first :)

And for the record, I am all for consolidation of the factions for the
moment. Perhaps Hydras could have userped control of the Bushido Predacons
and such, and others, while the other Maximal clans come together under one
banner?? Food for thought! :)

Anyways, game on!

Preston




